        <p>Virtual Run for a Cause: Date: 25 May 2024, Location:Africa Anywhere Get your running shoes ready for our Virtual Run for a Cause. This event allows participants from around the world to run or walk at their own pace and in their preferred location. Register on our website, set your fundraising goal, and encourage friends and family to sponsor your efforts. It's a fun and active way to make a difference while promoting health and fitness.</p>
